@startuml
[*] --> HomePage [Homepage loaded]
HomePage --> ProjectsPage [User selects "Projects"]
ProjectsPage --> PhotoView [User chooses "Photos"]
PhotoView --> ProjectsPage [User exits view]
ProjectsPage --> VideoView [User chooses "Videos"]
VideoView --> ProjectsPage [User exits view]
HomePage --> CareerOpportunitiesPage [User selects "Career Opportunities"]
CareerOpportunitiesPage --> UpdateView [User chooses "Updates"]
UpdateView --> CareerOpportunitiesPage [User exits view]
CareerOpportunitiesPage --> ApplicationForm [User chooses "Apply Now"]
ApplicationForm --> CareerOpportunitiesPage [User submits form]
ApplicationForm --> ReviewQueue [User submits form, system checks application]
ReviewQueue --> Approved [System approves application]
ReviewQueue --> Rejected [System rejects application]
@enduml
